      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p>This resolution recognizes the importance of fully funding the Department of Homeland Security (DHS).</p><p>The resolution also (1) cautions that Americans are at greater risk each day&nbsp;DHS is subject to a lapse in appropriations, and (2) expresses gratitude to DHS employees for their commitment to protect the United States.&nbsp;</p>",
